---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";

// import CTABook from '@components/CTA-Book.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Swiss Paraglide Zermatt - Tandem Paragliding Flights in front of the Matterhorn."
>
  <main>
    <div class="bg-white">
      <div
        class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 py-24 sm:px-6 sm:py-32 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8"
      >
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <h1 id="features-heading" class="font-medium text-gray-700">
            Pre-flight
          </h1>
          <h2
            class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl"
          >
            Good to know before you book a flight with Swiss Paraglide Zermatt.
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
            General information for your tandem paragliding flight in Zermatt.
            This will help you to prepare for your flight and to know what to
            expect. Safety is our top priority, and wind/weather conditions
            along with the fitness and confidence of the passenger all play a
            role our the decision to fly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="mt-11 grid grid-cols-1 items-start gap-x-6 gap-y-16 sm:mt-16 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 lg:gap-x-8 text-sm font-light text-black"
        >
          <div class="flex flex-col-reverse">
            <div class="mt-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium drop-shadow-md">Weather</h3>
              <p class="mt-2">
                We handle providing you with a safe and enjoyable flight &ndash;
                you're in charge of organising the beautiful flying weather :-)
              </p>
              <p class="mt-2">
                It goes without saying that Paragliding is absolutely, utterly
                weather dependant &ndash; the Weather Gods are in charge. If we
                are not able to fly due to poor weather conditions, you will not
                be charged for the Paragliding.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="aspect-h-1 aspect-w-1 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100"
            >
              <svg
                class="p-16"
                width="32"
                height="32"
                viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
                fill="currentColor"
                aria-hidden="true"
                focusable="false"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                clip-rule="evenodd"
              >
                <path
                  d="M500-40q-20 0-35-14.5t-15-34.77q0-9.73 3.5-18.23T464-123l36-33 36 33q7 7 10.5 15.735Q550-98.529 550-89q0 20-15 34.5T500-40Zm-141-65-35-35 111-111 35 35-111 111Zm261-57-53-53 53-53 53 53-53 53Zm-360 0-53-53 53-53 53 53-53 53Zm30-178q-86.864 0-148.432-61.52Q80-463.04 80-549.835 80-629 136.5-691 193-753 277-759q32-56 84.5-88.5T480.423-880Q571-880 632.5-822.5T708-680q79 4 125.5 53.5T880-510.377Q880-440 830.417-390 780.833-340 710-340H290Zm0-60h420q46.2 0 78.1-32.5 31.9-32.5 31.9-78T788.1-588q-31.9-32-78.1-32h-60v-30q0-71-49.5-120.5T480.212-820q-51.481 0-93.847 27.5Q344-765 324-718l-8 18h-28q-62 2-105 45.393t-43 104.464Q140-488 183.929-444 227.857-400 290-400Zm190-210Z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col-reverse">
            <div class="mt-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium drop-shadow-md">Fitness</h3>
              <p class="mt-2">
                You need to be good on your feet and able to run 10-20 steps
                with confidence on the start! It's particularly important that
                you follow the pilot's instructions at the take off (it's easy,
                but your pilot can't run for you).
              </p>
              <p class="mt-2">
                If you are older, heavier and/or have physical issues that
                affect being able to run, then please let us know &ndash; we
                will do our best, but as always, safety first!
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="aspect-h-1 aspect-w-1 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100"
            >
              <svg
                class="p-16"
                width="32"
                height="32"
                viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
                fill="currentColor"
                aria-hidden="true"
                focusable="false"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                clip-rule="evenodd"
              >
                <path
                  d="m550-84-42-42 142-142-382-382-142 142-42-42 56-58-56-56 85-85-42-42 42-42 43 41 84-84 56 56 58-56 42 42-142 142 382 382 142-142 42 42-56 58 56 56-86 86 42 42-42 42-42-42-84 84-56-56-58 56Z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col-reverse">
            <div class="mt-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium drop-shadow-md">Age</h3>
              <p class="mt-2">
                If you are between the ages of 5 to 69 and you meet our fitness
                criteria (see 'Fitness'), we'll be happy to take you for an
                amazing paragliding flight here in front of the Matterhorn.
              </p>
              <p class="mt-2">
                We can make the occasional exception if you are fit &amp; sporty
                beyond your years, but we reserve the final judgement (if this
                is the case, please contact us and let us know).
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="aspect-h-1 aspect-w-1 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100"
            >
              <svg
                class="p-16"
                width="32"
                height="32"
                viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
                fill="currentColor"
                aria-hidden="true"
                focusable="false"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                clip-rule="evenodd"
              >
                <path
                  d="M535-40v-239l-108-99-42 188-265-55 11-56 199 40 73-369-100 47v134h-60v-175l164-69q32-14 45.5-17.5T480-714q20 0 35.5 8.5T542-680l42 67q26 42 71 73t105 31v60q-67 0-119.5-31T543-573l-39 158 91 84v291h-60Zm5-714q-30 0-51.5-21.5T467-827q0-30 21.5-51.5T540-900q30 0 51.5 21.5T613-827q0 30-21.5 51.5T540-754Z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col-reverse">
            <div class="mt-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium drop-shadow-md">Safety</h3>
              <p class="mt-2">
                Going for a tandem paragliding flight in Switzerland is quite a
                safe activity. The Swiss Tandem Paragliding license is very
                highly rated and issued by the Swiss Aviation Authority.
              </p>
              <p class="mt-2">
                That said, we are going flying in the highest mountains in the
                Swiss Alps and there will always remain a small amount of risk
                (your pilot is flying with you and is also very interested in a
                fun, safe flight).
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="aspect-h-1 aspect-w-1 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100"
            >
              <svg
                class="p-16"
                width="32"
                height="32"
                viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
                fill="currentColor"
                aria-hidden="true"
                focusable="false"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                clip-rule="evenodd"
              >
                <path
                  d="M290-240h60v-90h90v-60h-90v-90h-60v90h-90v60h90v90Zm230-150h240v-40H520v40Zm0 120h160v-40H520v40ZM140-80q-24 0-42-18t-18-42v-480q0-24 18-42t42-18h250v-140q0-24 18-42t42.411-18h59.178Q534-880 552-862t18 42v140h250q24 0 42 18t18 42v480q0 24-18 42t-42 18H140Zm0-60h680v-480H570v30q0 28-18 44t-42.411 16h-59.178Q426-530 408-546t-18-44v-30H140v480Zm310-450h60v-230h-60v230Zm30 210Z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col-reverse">
            <div class="mt-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium drop-shadow-md">
                Photos & Videos
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2">
                Your pilot will use a specially designed (for amazing shots &
                safety) GoPro to capture unforgetable photos & videos of your
                flight. (+40.- CHF option)
              </p>
              <p class="mt-2">
                Phones and Selfie Sticks are not allowed &ndash; for safety
                reasons &ndash; nothing is allowed to fall during your flight...
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="aspect-h-1 aspect-w-1 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100"
            >
              <svg
                class="p-16"
                width="32"
                height="32"
                viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
                fill="currentColor"
                aria-hidden="true"
                focusable="false"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                clip-rule="evenodd"
              >
                <path
                  d="M479.5-267q72.5 0 121.5-49t49-121.5q0-72.5-49-121T479.5-607q-72.5 0-121 48.5t-48.5 121q0 72.5 48.5 121.5t121 49Zm0-60q-47.5 0-78.5-31.5t-31-79q0-47.5 31-78.5t78.5-31q47.5 0 79 31t31.5 78.5q0 47.5-31.5 79t-79 31.5ZM140-120q-24 0-42-18t-18-42v-513q0-23 18-41.5t42-18.5h147l73-87h240l73 87h147q23 0 41.5 18.5T880-693v513q0 24-18.5 42T820-120H140Zm0-60h680v-513H645l-73-87H388l-73 87H140v513Zm340-257Z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col-reverse">
            <div class="mt-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium drop-shadow-md">Transport</h3>
              <p class="mt-2">
                Our prices reflect the price of the Paragliding Flight only. If
                you do not have a valid Ski Pass and/or Peak Pass, you will need
                to purchase a lift ticket to reach the take off area.
              </p>
              <p class="mt-2">
                It's best to buy your ticket together with your pilot at the
                lift station, to prevent purchasing an incorrect pass.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="aspect-h-1 aspect-w-1 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100"
            >
              <svg
                class="p-16"
                width="32"
                height="32"
                viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
                fill="currentColor"
                aria-hidden="true"
                focusable="false"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                clip-rule="evenodd"
              >
                <path
                  d="M160-340v-380q0-41 19-71.5t58.5-50q39.5-19.5 100-29T480-880q86 0 146.5 9t99 28.5Q764-823 782-793t18 73v380q0 59-40.5 99.5T660-200l60 60v20h-70l-80-80H390l-80 80h-70v-20l60-60q-59 0-99.5-40.5T160-340Zm320-480q-120 0-173 15.5T231-760h501q-18-27-76.5-43.5T480-820ZM220-545h234v-155H220v155Zm440 60H220h520-80Zm-146-60h226v-155H514v155ZM335-315q23 0 39-16t16-39q0-23-16-39t-39-16q-23 0-39 16t-16 39q0 23 16 39t39 16Zm290 0q23 0 39-16t16-39q0-23-16-39t-39-16q-23 0-39 16t-16 39q0 23 16 39t39 16Zm-325 60h360q34 0 57-25t23-60v-145H220v145q0 35 23 60t57 25Zm180-505h252-501 249Z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col-reverse">
            <div class="mt-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium drop-shadow-md">Meeting Point</h3>

              <p class="mt-2">
                Winter Flights meet at the bottom of the Sunnegga/Rothorn
                lift, along the river in Zermatt. Winter Flights are from Dec
                1st unitl the Ski Lifts close for the winter (usually around
                April 20th).
              </p>
              <p class="mt-2">
                For Summer Flights the meeting point is in front of the Gornergrat
                Railway station in Zermatt (directly across from Zermatt's Main
                Train Station). Summer Flights are from the closing of the
                Winter ski lifts (end of April), until the end of November.
              </p>

            </div>

            <div
              class="aspect-h-1 aspect-w-1 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100"
            >
              <svg
                class="p-16"
                width="32"
                height="32"
                viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
                fill="currentColor"
                aria-hidden="true"
                focusable="false"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                clip-rule="evenodd"
              >
                <path
                  d="M468-240q-96-5-162-74t-66-166q0-100 70-170t170-70q97 0 166 66t74 163l-63-20q-11-64-60-106.5T480-660q-75 0-127.5 52.5T300-480q0 67 42.5 116.5T449-303l19 63Zm48 158q-9 1-18 1.5t-18 .5q-83 0-156-31.5T197-197q-54-54-85.5-127T80-480q0-83 31.5-156T197-763q54-54 127-85.5T480-880q83 0 156 31.5T763-763q54 54 85.5 127T880-480q0 9-.5 18t-1.5 18l-58-18v-18q0-142-99-241t-241-99q-142 0-241 99t-99 241q0 142 99 241t241 99h18l18 58Zm305 22L650-231 600-80 480-480l400 120-151 50 171 171-79 79Z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col-reverse">
            <div class="mt-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium drop-shadow-md">Cancelation</h3>
              <p class="mt-2">
                Flights can be cancelled with no charge, up to 12:00 noon on the
                day before the flight is scheduled. After this you will be
                charged the full amount. Please be on time for your meeting at
                the agreed upon Meeting Point.
              </p>
              <p class="mt-2">
                As with a normal airline ticket, if you're too late, the plane
                willl have left the Gate and you'll be charged.
              </p>
              <a
                class="block mt-2 font-medium underline"
                href="/terms-and-conditions"
                >Terms &amp; Conditions for details...<span class="sr-only">
                  about Cancelation</span
                >
              </a>
            </div>
            <div
              class="aspect-h-1 aspect-w-1 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100"
            >
              <svg
                class="p-16"
                width="32"
                height="32"
                viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
                fill="currentColor"
                aria-hidden="true"
                focusable="false"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                clip-rule="evenodd"
              >
                <path
                  d="m330-288 150-150 150 150 42-42-150-150 150-150-42-42-150 150-150-150-42 42 150 150-150 150 42 42ZM480-80q-82 0-155-31.5t-127.5-86Q143-252 111.5-325T80-480q0-83 31.5-156t86-127Q252-817 325-848.5T480-880q83 0 156 31.5T763-763q54 54 85.5 127T880-480q0 82-31.5 155T763-197.5q-54 54.5-127 86T480-80Zm0-60q142 0 241-99.5T820-480q0-142-99-241t-241-99q-141 0-240.5 99T140-480q0 141 99.5 240.5T480-140Zm0-340Z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <style></style>
</Layout>
